snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday - “Thor odinson Will Return” Trailer | Chris Hemsworth (Concept Version)
snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— Avengers: Doomsday - Thor odinson Will Return

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, the story reframes the coming conflict through the weight of legacy and responsibility rather than spectacle, centering on a world where familiar heroes are no longer driven by glory but by what they stand to lose. As the multiversal order begins to fracture under an unseen but deliberate hand, the Avengers are forced to confront a threat that challenges not only their strength, but their purpose. Thor’s journey anchors the narrative, revealing a god who has fought for realms and crowns now facing a far more human fear: the need to protect a future embodied in a single child. snippet.title: Berlin — Take My Breath Away (Sub. Español / Lyrics)
snippet.description:
Berlin — Take My Breath Away
Español / Lyrics ✨

╰► 𝗕𝗔𝗦𝗜𝗖 𝗜𝗡𝗙𝗢 ❥
Berlin - Take My Breath Away - Love Theme from "Top Gun"
Released 1986/Junio/09
#Berlin #rock #indie #poprock #alternativo #old #takemybreathaway 

🌅 Imagen de fondo: (aquí va la imagen, que no se te olvide)

💿 Sigue al artista: 
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7qy5N8yYDm6psRHiJDT09Q

🍃 Sígueme a mí (chi?)
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/richii.almazan/
Canal Principal:
____________________________________

Lyrics de la canción :D
[Verse 1]
Watching every motion in my foolish lover's game
On this endless ocean, finally lovers know no shame
Turning and returning to some secret place inside
Watching in slow motion as you turn around and say

[Chorus]
"Take my breath away"
"Take my breath away"

[Verse 2]
Watching, I keep waiting, still anticipating love
Never hesitating to become the fated ones
Turning and returning to some secret place to hide
Watching in slow motion as you turn to me and say

[Chorus]
"My love, take my breath away"

[Bridge]
Through the hourglass, I saw you
In time, you slipped away
When the mirror crashed I called you
And turned to hear you say
"If only for today, I am unafraid"

[Verse 3]
Watching every motion in this foolish lover's game
Haunted by the notion somewhere there's a love in flames
Turning and returning to some secret place inside
Watching in slow motion as you turn my way and say

[Chorus]
"Take my breath away"
"My love, take my breath away"
"My love, take my breath away, my love"
"My love, take my breath away, my love"
"Take my breath away..."

____________________________________

One of the most captivating visions of the Marvel mythos is coming to an end! The final days of the Ultimate Universe, the acclaimed line of titles that ignited the industry over the last two years, begins on December 31 in ULTIMATE ENDGAME. The five-issue event series by Ultimates writer Deniz Camp and superstar artists Jonas Scharf and Terry Dodson brings the Ultimate series together for the long-awaited showdown with the architect behind this twisted universe, the Maker.
